Third floor (used to be staff bathroom) It is next to the boy's bathroom. If you are going up the atrium stairs it is to your left and then down the hall to the left. There is windows across from the bathroom. 
You can also use the nurses office bathroom (little door with window across from Fieldhouse).
Or the gendered bathrooms near the pool/dance hallway are usually not as busy as the cafteria ones (GENDERED THOUGH)
comment: Not everyone knows of this bathroom, lets keep it secret for lgbt only please. If you want more information please see Mrs.Thompson the CCRC (near the cafeteria across form the counselors office) Woman staff member with black short hair. She runs the AS-IS(gay-straight alliance) group which when I went to york was afterschool on wednesdays in the CCRC.
